OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Activists in Catalonia are celebrating 
OL,6, after the government of the Spanish    
OL,7, region informed its town and city halls
OL,8, that they must allow women to go       
OL,9, topless in public swimming pools.      
OL,11,FGoing topless is enshrined under a 2020
OL,12,FCatalan equality law.                  
OL,14,FHowever, some municipal swimming pools 
OL,15,Fhave prevented the practice since the  
OL,16,Flegislation was introduced, drawing    
OL,17,Fdozens of complaints each summer.      
OL,19,FLocal authorities have now been told to
OL,20,Fbar any form of discrimination.        
